text: Kevin Jeffery Lincoln II (born October 28, 1980) is an American politician and pastor who was the mayor of Stockton, California from 2021 to 2025. Kevin Jeffery Lincoln was born October 28, 1980, in San Joaquin County, and raised in Stockton. His mother was of Mexican descent and his father was African American. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Stockton, California Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
